<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Role Change Approval</title>
</head>

<body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
    <div
        style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <h1 style="color: #2c3e50; border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db; padding-bottom: 10px;">Role Change Approved</h1>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <img src="https://www.vecteezy.com/vector-art/14563653-team-target-or-achievement-teamwork-or-leadership-to-lead-to-achieve-goal-business-direction-or-success-career-path-or-growth-concept-flat-vector-modern-illustration"
                alt="Role Change Approval Illustration" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; max-width: 100%;">
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 16px;">We are pleased to inform you that your request to change your role to <strong
                style="color: #3498db;">
                <%= role %>
            </strong> has been approved.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px;">You can now access the additional features and responsibilities associated with this
            role.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px;">Thank you for your dedication and hard work.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 20px; font-style: italic;">
            <p style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Best regards,</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0;">The Plana Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>